      "id": 1917,
      "sender_id": 25,
      "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"117\">@Gan W.</span> Thanks, good point. We will include NumPy.</p>\n<p>More generally, third-party packages can be added to the sandbox as long as they do not affect fairness, reproducibility, or security.</p>\n<p>Please propose any packages you would like to use in this Zulip topic. For specific requests, opening a GitHub issue is also welcome.</p>\n<p>We will share the approved package list with versions.</p>",
